# CancellationsStore

The `CancellationsStore` is a typescript class that contains `svelte` stores, to which you can subscribe to get reactive updates in your elements.

```js
import { CancellationsStore, CancellationsClient } from "@holochain-open-dev/profiles";

const store = new CancellationsStore(new CancellationsClient(appAgentClient, 'my-role-name'));
```

> Learn how to setup the `AppAgentClient` object [here](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@holochain/client).

Learn more about the stores and how to integrate them in different frameworks [here](https://holochain-open-dev.github.io/reusable-modules/frontend/using/#stores).
